TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {35843=This action corrects a final rule; technical amendment, published in the Federal Register on December 15, 2014, that made minor adjustments to the boundary descriptions of restricted areas R-2932, R-2933, R-2934 and R-2935 at Cape Canaveral, FL. Due to a submission error, one latitude/longitude point was omitted from the description of restricted area R-2935, Cape Canaveral, FL. This action corrects the boundary description of R-2935 by adding the missing point., 38809=Title 14 published on 2015-01-01, 31667=This action removes restricted area R-2936, West Palm Beach, FL. The using agency informed the FAA they no longer have a requirement for this area; therefore, the airspace is being returned to the National Airspace System (NAS)., 13181=This action corrects a final rule; technical amendment, published in the Federal Register on April 7, 2015, that made a correction to a typographical error to R-6703A, R-6703B, R-6703C, R-6703D, R-6703E and R-6703F at Joint Base Lewis-McChord, WA. Due to a submission error, the abbreviation for West in the longitude description of restricted area R-6703A was entered as “N”. This action corrects the boundary description of R-6703A by changing the longitude direction to “W”.}

textAfterTable: DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION, Federal Aviation Administration Final rule; technical amendment. Effective date: 0901 UTC, August 20, 2015. 14 CFR Part 73 Summary This action amends Title 14 Code of Federal Regulations (14 CFR) part 73 by making an editorial change to the location names listed in the titles of restricted areas R-5301, R-5302A, R-5302B, and R-5302C in North Carolina. There are no changes to the boundaries; designated altitudes; time of designation, activities conducted within the restricted areas or the actual physical locations of the restricted areas. 2015-05-26; vol. 80 # 100 - Tuesday, May 26, 2015 80 FR 29941 - Modification of Restricted Areas R-4501A, R-4501B, R-4501C, R-4501D, R-4501F, and R-4501H; Fort Leonard Wood, MO GPO FDSys XML | Text Additional Documents type regulations.gov FR Doc. 2015-12627
